snippet.title: Mulaka - Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
Pre-order now on Nintendo Switch & Xbox One!

Mulaka lands on PlayStation 4 and Steam on February 27th, 2018, followed by Nintendo Switch on March 1st, and Xbox One on March 2nd.

Dive into northern Mexico's breathtaking landscapes with Mulaka, a 3D action-adventure game based on the rich indigenous culture of the Tarahumara.

Learn more at www.lienzo.mx/mulaka
